{
  "slug": "sgraffito-landscape-tile-air-dry",
  "title": "Sgraffito Landscape Tile in Air-Dry Clay",
  "subtitle": "Scratch a simple landscape through white slip to reveal the clay below",
  "excerpt": "Apply white slip to a leather-hard clay tile, allow it to stiffen, then scratch back through it with a needle tool to reveal the contrasting clay body beneath. The result is a two-tone landscape drawing fired into the surface of the tile -- without a kiln.",
